Assignment 1.05 by Patrick McCartney based on solution to 1.04 by Professor Scheaffer

Uses ncurses to get input from the user for each turn and print to a 24x81 window

Displays the PC position on the first line, line 23 displays the incorrect key (if incorrect input is given).
Required keys are implemented, but note that exiting from monster list takes a few seconds for some odd reason.